location.fullValue: Pendleton Plan, Single Family Collection at Snowden Bridge

data.description: This move-in ready townhome is located in the Snowden Bridge community, near the new Frederick County Elementary School. It offers 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. The community has a range of amenities for residents to enjoy, including a pool for swimming, an indoor rec center for playing tennis, and two playgrounds for families. These amenities are just steps away from the front door, providing ample options for recreational activities. The main level of the townhome features a spacious family room, kitchen, and dining area. There is also a nice deck, perfect for entertaining. The primary bedroom has an en suite bathroom and a large walk-in closet. There are additional bedrooms and a hall bathroom on the second level, as well as a convenient laundry area. The lower level of the townhome includes a movie room or office space, as well as a 2-car garage    Call today to schedule a tour of this move-in ready townhome in Snowden Bridge!
